{"tid":1855082,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"用口罩加一罐午餐肉溝到女","createTime":"2020-02-01T01:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T01:44:42.000Z","uid":242537,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f80f7938fa137b806496fe8e64178faf87a29314","tid":1855082,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T01:16:00.000Z","msg":"前幾晚行行下街見到個短裙MK妹無戴口罩，我咪問佢做咩唔帶，佢話屋企無曬，我拿拿林拎左我背襄入面個個口罩同一罐午餐肉比佢，佢好開心同我講多謝，仲交換埋電話添<br />\n<br />\n尋晚我發whatsapp 問佢仲要唔要，我有一盒可以拎比佢，佢叫我拎上佢屋企，仲煮埋飯比我食 煎香埋罐午餐肉一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果拎住盒口罩上到佢屋企，食完飯，飲左陣酒吹左陣水<br />\n<br />\n最後搞埋 中出 為左響應環保少女how dare you 唔戴套中出左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1db2e11332df8ea961d3f53ca0525e6d1c1ea55","tid":1855082,"uid":105207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T01:19:24.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"85e75692014112751b616d660c75388c0a34108c","tid":1855082,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T01:21:50.000Z","msg":"幫手簽，同埋搵多十個人簽丫唔該，好快簽夠數架喇，記住搵多十個人簽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Iq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=d78038e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a>"},{"pid":"792dae0c5d1a1